{"tid":1748740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"｛重要｝防暴警察票站內拍攝犯法","createTime":"2019-11-23T21:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T23:24:34.000Z","uid":265893,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"98c3e253aaf7b565d3db55f678459b9785475567","tid":1748740,"uid":265893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T21:29:54.000Z","msg":"【手動轉】請臨時拉伕 #又唔做嘢 #又唔讀書 嘅防暴留意。<br />\n<br />\n根據 Cap 541F r. 48，投票站內警員有權用電子儀器通訊（候選人、代理人、選民不可以），但任何人（包括警察）未經投票站主任/選舉主任或選管會成員的明示准許 (express permission) 而拍攝、錄音、錄影，即屬違法，最高可判監 6 個月及罰款。"},{"pid":"b280f91f9c09ec245af74a1bad49bc052a14b5db","tid":1748740,"uid":58453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T22:58:12.000Z","msg":"屌 咁佢地實話有受權比黑驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90e0d9234d2799b6b31e26616694c8af8e25a68","tid":1748740,"uid":70008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T23:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83e647ddc48931ce0b3692b30bf9e89b5939e31","tid":1748740,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T23:24:34.000Z","msg":"實話選舉主任俾佢地影<br />\n放心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}